export const docsHtml = "<h1>OpenApe IdP — flows</h1>\n<p>How a user gets an identity on this DDISA Identity Provider. Screenshots are\ncaptured live from the containerized E2E stack (<code>compose/demo/run.sh</code>) and\nrefreshed on every run.</p>\n<h2>Passkey sign-up</h2>\n<p>A new user registers a <strong>WebAuthn passkey</strong> — no password. The IdP becomes the\nDDISA authority for their identity; Service Providers (Troop, Chat, …) then log\nthem in via DNS-discovered SSO without ever seeing a credential.</p>\n<p>The IdP landing page (enter your email to start):</p>\n<p><img src=\"/docs/screenshots/01-idp-landing.png\" alt=\"IdP landing\"></p>\n<p>A registration link is issued (the email a real user receives):</p>\n<p><img src=\"/docs/screenshots/02-idp-request-link.png\" alt=\"Registration link\"></p>\n<p>Registering the passkey (<code>/register?token=…</code>) — a CDP virtual authenticator\nanswers the ceremony headlessly in the E2E run:</p>\n<p><img src=\"/docs/screenshots/03-idp-register-passkey.png\" alt=\"Passkey registration\"></p>\n<h2>Account dashboard</h2>\n<p>Signed in — the IdP account dashboard, where the user manages passkeys, agents,\npermissions and connected services:</p>\n<p><img src=\"/docs/screenshots/04-idp-registered.png\" alt=\"IdP dashboard\"></p>\n"
